cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE. 

This paper is about enhancing neural networks with knowledge graphs and ontologies for better performance on question answering tasks. The most relevant sub-category is likely cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and understanding. Other relevant sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) for the use of neural networks, cs.LG (Machine Learning) for the pretraining and fine-tuning of the model, cs.IR (Information Retrieval) for the question answering task, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) for the use of neural networks.
